    .row
      %img{:src => '/images/roomhirepic.jpg', :style=> 'width: 960px;'}
      .col-xs-12
        %h1
          Hire a Room
      .row
      .col-xs-12
        %p Are you looking for a Covid-secure meeting, conference or training room to hire with socially-distanced lay-outs, safe guidelines for you to follow, refreshments available, free WiFi and free on-site parking? All rooms are wheelchair accessible.
        %h2 Capacities and Costs
        %p
          <b>Blue Room</B> - a spacious room that seats 10 in a circle or 12 facing the front. Cost is £20 per hour or £100 per day. 
        %p
          <b>Green Room</B> - a fresh and homely room that seats 8 in a circle or 7 facing the front. Cost is £15 per hour or £75 per day.
        %p
          <b>Yellow Room</B> - a smaller room with lower ceilings that sits 8 in a circle or 6 facing the front. Cost is £12 per hour or £60 per day.
        %p
          <b>The Cafe Studio</B> - a lovely large well ventilated studio-like space with a capacity of 15-30 people (depending on lay-out), Cost is £25 per hour or £150 per day.
        %p
          <b>Main Hall</B> - a large hall with stage with a capacity of 30 people (2m apart) or 60 people (1m apart so must keep face coverings on throughout) in rows facing the front. Cost is £30 per hour or £180 per day.
        %p
          <b>Purple Room</b> - a comfortable spacious meeting room with a meeting table and comfortable sofas/chairs to accomodate 4 people. Cost is £12 per hour or £60 per day.
        %p
          We are very happy to be flexible with our spaces and discuss your room lay-out or furniture requests. 
        %p
        %h2 refreshments
        %p 
          We would love to discuss your refreshment requirements, ranging from providing a table and hot water for you, to fully catered tea, coffee and lunches. We have modern well-equipped kitchens easily accesible from all rooms.
        %h2 are you a charity
        %p 
          We offer a 20% discount to charities so please do give your registered charity number when you make a booking.
        %h2 equipment
        %p
          We can provide individual tables for participants or trestle tables. 
        %p
          Our rooms have good quality large TV screens, to which you can connect a laptop. We can also offer flip-charts and pens, white boards in some rooms and an auditorium Sound & AV system in the Main hall. 
        %h2 get in touch
        %p 
          We'd love to discuss your requirements with you. Please do contact us -
          %a{:href => 'mailto:admin@streamsofhope.org.uk'} send an email 
          or give us a call on 01962 863 217 and leave a message. We will get back to you as quickly as possible.
